      <h1>ChatGPT vs Microsoft Copilot: Which AI Assistant Is Better in 2026?</h1>
      <p class="meta">Updated June 2026</p>
    </header>

    <p class="lead">
      If you are choosing between ChatGPT and Microsoft Copilot in 2026, you are comparing two leading solutions that serve millions of users worldwide. Both products have matured significantly and offer unique strengths for different use cases. After extensive hands-on testing across performance benchmarks, real-world workflows, and long-term usage scenarios, here is the detailed comparison you need to make an informed decision.
    </p>

